{"comments":"Color space conversions for picker/wheel synchronization.\n\n**BIDIRECTIONAL SYNC REQUIREMENT:**\nWhen a user adjusts any color property (hue slider, RGB input, hex code),\nALL representations must update synchronously. This module provides the\nmathematical conversions to maintain consistency across color spaces.\n\n**Use case: Playground color picker**\n1. User adjusts Hue slider (0-359)\n2. HSL updates → rgbToHsl converts → RGB updates\n3. RGB updates → rgbToHex converts → Hex display updates\n4. All views show the same color, zero drift\n\n**Color space conversions:**\n- HSL ↔ RGB (color wheel ↔ display values)\n- RGB ↔ CMYK (screen ↔ print)\n- RGB ↔ Hex (code ↔ human-readable)\n- Kelvin → RGB (temperature ↔ display)\n\n**Billion-agent scale requirement:**\nAll conversions use industry-standard algorithms. Two agents converting\nthe same color will get identical results (within floating point precision).\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Convert HSL to RGB\n\nUses standard HSL → RGB algorithm:\n1. Convert HSL percentages to 0-1 range\n2. Calculate chroma and intermediate values\n3. Map to RGB cube\n\n```purescript\nhslToRgb (HSL.hsl 0 100 50)     -- Pure red: RGB(255, 0, 0)\nhslToRgb (HSL.hsl 120 100 50)   -- Pure green: RGB(0, 255, 0)\nhslToRgb (HSL.hsl 240 100 50)   -- Pure blue: RGB(0, 0, 255)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HSL"],"HSL"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[157,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[157,1]},"title":"hslToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert RGB to HSL\n\nUses standard RGB → HSL algorithm:\n1. Normalize RGB to 0-1 range\n2. Find min, max, delta\n3. Calculate hue, saturation, lightness\n\n```purescript\nrgbToHsl (RGB.rgb 255 0 0)   -- HSL(0°, 100%, 50%) - red\nrgbToHsl (RGB.rgb 128 128 128) -- HSL(0°, 0%, 50%) - gray\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HSL"],"HSL"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[196,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[196,1]},"title":"rgbToHsl"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert RGB to CMYK (screen to print)\n\nUses standard RGB → CMYK algorithm:\n1. Normalize RGB to 0-1 range\n2. Calculate K (black key) = 1 - max(R, G, B)\n3. If K = 1 (pure black), C=M=Y=0\n4. Otherwise: C = (1-R-K)/(1-K), same for M and Y\n\n```purescript\nrgbToCmyk (RGB.rgb 255 0 0)    -- CMYK(0, 100, 100, 0) - red\nrgbToCmyk (RGB.rgb 0 0 0)      -- CMYK(0, 0, 0, 100) - black\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CMYK"],"CMYK"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[249,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[249,1]},"title":"rgbToCmyk"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert CMYK to RGB (print to screen)\n\nUses standard CMYK → RGB algorithm:\n1. R = 255 * (1 - C) * (1 - K)\n2. G = 255 * (1 - M) * (1 - K)\n3. B = 255 * (1 - Y) * (1 - K)\n\n```purescript\ncmykToRgb (CMYK.cmyk 0 100 100 0)  -- RGB(255, 0, 0) - red\ncmykToRgb (CMYK.cmyk 0 0 0 100)    -- RGB(0, 0, 0) - black\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","CMYK"],"CMYK"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[287,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[287,1]},"title":"cmykToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert RGB to hex string\n\nReturns 6-character hex string (no # prefix).\nAgents can prepend # if needed for CSS/HTML contexts.\n\n```purescript\nrgbToHex (RGB.rgb 255 0 0)     -- \"FF0000\"\nrgbToHex (RGB.rgb 128 128 128) -- \"808080\"\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[314,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[314,1]},"title":"rgbToHex"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert hex string to RGB\n\nAccepts formats:\n- \"FF0000\" (6 chars)\n- \"#FF0000\" (7 chars with #)\n- \"F00\" (3 chars, expands to FF0000)\n- \"#F00\" (4 chars with #)\n\nInvalid hex returns black RGB(0, 0, 0).\n\n```purescript\nhexToRgb \"FF0000\"   -- RGB(255, 0, 0)\nhexToRgb \"#FF0000\"  -- RGB(255, 0, 0)\nhexToRgb \"F00\"      -- RGB(255, 0, 0)\nhexToRgb \"invalid\"  -- RGB(0, 0, 0) - fallback\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"String"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[339,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[339,1]},"title":"hexToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert RGB to XYZ (device-dependent to device-independent)\n\nAssumes sRGB color space with D65 white point.\nSteps:\n1. Convert RGB 0-255 to 0-1\n2. Apply inverse sRGB companding (gamma correction)\n3. Apply sRGB → XYZ matrix transformation\n\n```purescript\nrgbToXyz (RGB.rgb 255 255 255)  -- D65 white point\nrgbToXyz (RGB.rgb 0 0 0)        -- Black\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","XYZ"],"XYZ"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[373,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[373,1]},"title":"rgbToXyz"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert XYZ to RGB (device-independent to device-dependent)\n\nAssumes sRGB color space with D65 white point.\nSteps:\n1. Apply XYZ → sRGB matrix transformation\n2. Apply sRGB companding (gamma correction)\n3. Convert 0-1 to RGB 0-255\n\n```purescript\nxyzToRgb XYZ.d65White  -- RGB(255, 255, 255)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","XYZ"],"XYZ"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[403,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[403,1]},"title":"xyzToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert XYZ to LAB (device-independent to perceptual)\n\nUses D65 white point and CIE standard formulas.\nThis is where the perceptual uniformity is created.\n\n```purescript\nxyzToLab XYZ.d65White  -- LAB(100, 0, 0) - white\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","XYZ"],"XYZ"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LAB"],"LAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[445,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[445,1]},"title":"xyzToLab"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert LAB to XYZ (perceptual to device-independent)\n\nInverse of xyzToLab.\n\n```purescript\nlabToXyz (LAB.lab 100.0 0.0 0.0)  -- D65 white point\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LAB"],"LAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","XYZ"],"XYZ"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[479,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[479,1]},"title":"labToXyz"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert RGB to LAB (convenience function)\n\nGoes through XYZ: RGB → XYZ → LAB\n\n```purescript\nrgbToLab (RGB.rgb 255 0 0)  -- Red in perceptual space\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LAB"],"LAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[522,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[522,1]},"title":"rgbToLab"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert LAB to RGB (convenience function)\n\nGoes through XYZ: LAB → XYZ → RGB\n\n```purescript\nlabToRgb (LAB.lab 50.0 80.0 67.0)  -- Perceptual red to display RGB\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LAB"],"LAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[532,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[532,1]},"title":"labToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert RGB to LCH (convenience function)\n\nGoes through XYZ and LAB: RGB → XYZ → LAB → LCH\n\n```purescript\nrgbToLch (RGB.rgb 255 0 0)  -- Red in cylindrical perceptual space\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LCH"],"LCH"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[546,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[546,1]},"title":"rgbToLch"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert LCH to RGB (convenience function)\n\nGoes through LAB and XYZ: LCH → LAB → XYZ → RGB\n\n```purescript\nlchToRgb (LCH.lch 50.0 100.0 0.0)  -- Perceptual cylindrical to display RGB\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","LCH"],"LCH"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[556,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[556,1]},"title":"lchToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert Kelvin color temperature to RGB\n\nRe-export from Kelvin module for convenience.\nUses Tanner Helland's algorithm for accurate temperature conversion.\n\n```purescript\nkelvinToRgb (K.kelvin 2700)  -- Warm tungsten light\nkelvinToRgb (K.kelvin 6500)  -- Cool daylight\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Kelvin"],"Kelvin"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[572,35],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[572,1]},"title":"kelvinToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"RGB → OKLAB (modern perceptual uniform space)\nUses linear RGB → LMS → OKLAB transformation\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLAB"],"OKLAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[704,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[704,1]},"title":"rgbToOklab"},{"children":[],"comments":"OKLAB → RGB\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLAB"],"OKLAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[737,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[737,1]},"title":"oklabToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"OKLAB → OKLCH (rectangular → cylindrical)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLAB"],"OKLAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLCH"],"OKLCH"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[775,43],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[775,1]},"title":"oklabToOklch"},{"children":[],"comments":"OKLCH → OKLAB (cylindrical → rectangular)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLCH"],"OKLCH"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLAB"],"OKLAB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[796,43],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[796,1]},"title":"oklchToOklab"},{"children":[],"comments":"RGB → OKLCH (convenience)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLCH"],"OKLCH"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[817,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[817,1]},"title":"rgbToOklch"},{"children":[],"comments":"OKLCH → RGB (convenience)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLCH"],"OKLCH"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[821,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[821,1]},"title":"oklchToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"RGB → HWB (direct conversion)\n\n**Algorithm:**\n- Hue: same as HSL hue (derived from RGB)\n- Whiteness: min(R, G, B) / 255 as percentage\n- Blackness: 1 - max(R, G, B) / 255 as percentage\n\nThis is a direct calculation, not via HSL intermediate.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HWB"],"HWB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[836,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[836,1]},"title":"rgbToHwb"},{"children":[],"comments":"HWB → RGB (direct conversion)\n\n**Algorithm:**\n1. If W + B >= 100: achromatic gray = W / (W + B)\n2. Otherwise: calculate pure hue RGB, then:\n   RGB' = RGB * (1 - W/100 - B/100) + W/100\n\nThis avoids HSL intermediate for better precision.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","HWB"],"HWB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[869,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[869,1]},"title":"hwbToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"RGB → YUV (video color space)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","YUV"],"YUV"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[910,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[910,1]},"title":"rgbToYuv"},{"children":[],"comments":"YUV → RGB\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","YUV"],"YUV"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[925,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[925,1]},"title":"yuvToRgb"},{"children":[],"comments":"RGB → Record (for JSON serialization / backend persistence)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["r",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["g",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["b",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[651,59],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Conversion.purs","start":[651,1]},"title":"rgbToRecord"},{"children":[],"comments":"Record → RGB (from JSON deserialization / backend)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["r",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["g",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["b",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGB"],"tag":"TypeConst